## Do Not Break

- App entry: `AuthGate` in `examspark_frontend/lib/main.dart`
- Canonical code: `examspark_frontend/lib/` only — no root `lib/` mirror
- **Never rewrite Supabase auth** — UI restyle only
- Keep `LectureService`, `RecordingService`, edge function wiring in Phase 2

## Implementation Rules

- Compare before deleting duplicate files; merge unique code first
- Never delete files without founder confirmation
- Every code task: Manual Setup Checklist + .env Checklist
- Update `examspark_frontend/ROADMAP.md` checkboxes when completing work

